{"tid":902874,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]點樣可以幫另一半減壓??","createTime":"2018-11-15T06:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T12:35:45.000Z","uid":22961,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"46e6a3dd04bcab302cc5210de56140b5e84d4ed9","tid":902874,"uid":22961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T06:21:03.000Z","msg":"我老公呢排返工好大壓力<br />\n因為人手唔夠 成日要OT 咩都要做 又要幫其他人執手尾<br />\n又要幫啲上頭做替死鬼 食死貓 揹鑊<br />\n佢近排成日唔夠時間休息 夜晚瞓瞓下又會醒左 之後瞓唔返 成晚失眠<br />\n日日見住佢放工返黎 格硬對住我擠出笑容 扮無事 我就好心痛<br />\n唔知有啲咩可以幫到佢 唔知有咩可以做到 幫佢減下壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我可以做咩氹下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9955c2f9ae03c2ec732e1d13b4781ef0e03c3de","tid":902874,"uid":112390,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T06:37:27.000Z","msg":"含"},{"pid":"794c408bae3679ce71024d81b0a41732bc1206a1","tid":902874,"uid":1590,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T06:45:46.000Z","msg":"照顧哂佢生活所有野，再加上啲佢平時中意既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9862326548029f29b80350ea34dababe1cedb71","tid":902874,"uid":22961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"794c408bae3679ce71024d81b0a41732bc1206a1","tid":902874,"uid":1590,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T06:45:46.000Z","msg":"照顧哂佢生活所有野，再加上啲佢平時中意既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T07:00:20.000Z","msg":"唉 日日見到我老公咁都唔知可以做啲咩<br />\n我都有盡量打理好屋企 希望佢返到黎就有飯食 有靚湯飲 屋企乾乾淨淨 整齊企理 想佢返到屋企有個好啲舒適嘅環境<br />\n有時想關心下佢工作點 佢又會驚我擔心 唔講太多 但我睇得出佢返工真係好大壓力 佢都好耐無好好咁放假休息<br />\n有時放假都會理工作嘅野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今晚試下同佢按摩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3e47b7e4ec136d58