/>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T10:24:10.000Z","msg":"其實唔洗驚煩到佢既，說話既方式問題<br />\n你可以俾選擇佢，同佢講：「如果你有咩唔開心、想呻，可以同我講，我會一直係到聽你講」<br />\n等佢知道你都想關心佢咁，但又唔係逼佢講咁。<br />\n<br />\n因為通常聽得多佢講、你會對佢工作環境越黎越清晰，咁聽聽下你就唔會係得個聽字、可以輕輕搭兩句嘴咁。<br />\n<br />\n除非你老公係盲毛，以為你做既所有野都係理所當然啦，咁就另計了。"},{"pid":"80283d73cb4b9c7556aab308c9e88a51d70be1bb","tid":902874,"uid":1590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T10:31:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d840086578a33ca556a88da0d7b47d351fd88437","tid":902874,"uid":22961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6bf5fdfc9c57f9ce2fac765a7d88a07be26a952","tid":902874,"uid":171119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T09:00:22.000Z","msg":"你拍拖個陣係點做架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T10:39:26.000Z","msg":"都係煮下佢鐘意食嘅野 買下小禮物咁<br />\n但佢近排係大壓力到 呢啲野都唔係好幫到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似連笑嘅力都無咁 日日都愁工作嘅野"},{"pid":"334d09d9688bf80652c9ad61a38a4b55108bf1fd","tid":902874,"uid":22961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80283d73cb4b9c7556aab308c9e88a51d70be1bb","tid":902874,"uid":1590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T10:31:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T10:42:23.000Z","msg":"我暫時未壞腦 都係煩點樣可以安慰佢<br />\n不過多謝你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都會好好處理下自己心態"},{"pid":"455afc0c8b062e6b0586cbf497fbad57a44d9b35","tid":902874,"uid":1590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"334d09d9688bf80652c9ad61a38a4b55108bf1fd","tid":902874,"uid":22961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80283d73cb4b9c7556aab308c9e88a51d70be1bb","tid":902874,"uid":1590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-1